Posts.Content: Hello everyone, my name is Jack and I have been fighting cancer since 2011, I had a robotic prostatectomy I am now having kidney issues, kidney not draining may need a stent put in, does anyone here have experience with that may I ask what your experience has been, it is believed that my tumors are now creating a partial blockage on my ureter tube that leads from my bladder to my kidney. thank guys peace to you all jack
Posts.Title: Advanced proststate cancer and Kidney problems
